    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "キッチンカーで営業してるジューススタンドから\nCM撮影の依頼、ですか？",
      "startTime": 3.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7666.666666599999,
          "startTime": 11.5333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。一日店長の仕事も同時にきていてな\nこれが先方から届いた資料だ",
      "startTime": 11.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、これ、今若い子の間で大人気のジューススタンド\n『ふれっしゅふれっしゅ』じゃないですか！",
      "startTime": 18.9881629307,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2833.333333399999,
          "startTime": 21.8214962641
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "ふむふむ……一日店長として新しいジュースの\nメニューを考案して欲しい……なるほど",
      "startTime": 28.0214967727,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "オリジナルメニュー考案なんて面白そうです！\nどんなジュースがいいのかなぁ……",
      "startTime": 37.388159879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "せっかく作るなら好きな果物のジュースが\nいいかなって思うんですけど、どう思いますか？",
      "startTime": 43.1214942296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "渚は確か桃が好きだったよな？\nだったら、桃を使ったジュースでいいんじゃないか",
      "startTime": 50,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか！？　やったぁ\n大好きな桃のジュースを作れるなんてワクワクします",
      "startTime": 56.1663732212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、材料も決まったことですし\n早速具体的なレシピを考えてみます！",
      "startTime": 63.6663732212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、今度寮のキッチンで\n一緒にいくつか試作してみようか",
      "startTime": 69.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "先に言っておいてくれれば、当日までにこっちで\nある程度の材料は用意しておくよ",
      "startTime": 74.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！　じゃあ、お客さんが喜んで\nくれそうなメニューをいくつか考えておきますね！",
      "startTime": 81.1126317662,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 85.4459650995,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1766.6666667000045,
          "startTime": 87.2126317662
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、こんにちは……\n……って、なんですかこの大量の桃は！？",
      "startTime": 90.5459650995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "クライアントの方が渚の大ファンだったらしくてな\nサンプルとして桃を沢山送ってくれたんだ",
      "startTime": 98.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんですね……！　どこを見ても桃だらけ……\nまるで天国です……！",
      "startTime": 107.5592075668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "渚が喜んでくれて良かったよ……\nあまりにも大量で食べきれるか分からないが",
      "startTime": 113.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です！　このくらいペロッと食べられます！\nせっかく送ってもらったので無駄には出来ませんし",
      "startTime": 120.5932703975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "早速、ファンのみんなに喜んでもらえる\n最高のオリジナルジュースを考えましょう！",
      "startTime": 127.1599380814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いつになく張り切ってるじゃないか\nそんなにやる気を出してくれて俺も嬉しいよ",
      "startTime": 133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "自分で考えたメニューを販売してもらえる\n機会なんてそうそうありませんから",
      "startTime": 139.083973249,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "しかも、大好きな桃を使ったジュースを作れるんです\nやる気が出ないはずがありませんよ！",
      "startTime": 146.383973249,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "今日という日に向けて、ちゃんといくつか\nレシピを考えてきましたし、準備万端です",
      "startTime": 151.6839590075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "桃も沢山あることですし、いろいろ試しましょう！\nそれじゃあ、まずは……",
      "startTime": 159.8172923408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、そっちの箱に入ってる桃の\n皮むきとカットをお願いしてもいいですか？",
      "startTime": 164.7506256742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、任せてくれ\n……カットした桃はここに並べていくぞ",
      "startTime": 169.8333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cooking-04.m4a",
          "delay": 6495.950094499989,
          "startTime": 174.2
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cooking-04.m4a",
          "delay": 5262.616761200007,
          "startTime": 172.9666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cooking-04.m4a",
          "delay": 7729.283427799999,
          "startTime": 175.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "わあ……どれもちょうど良く熟してて\nすっごく美味しそうです！",
      "startTime": 176.4886621001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-ngs019.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとだけ味見しちゃいますね\nジュースに使うには、味が大事ですから！",
      "startTime": 182.3219832264,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-ngs020.m4a",
      "text": "もぐもぐ……ん～、美味しい～！　よーし、こっちのも\n味見を……ん、さっきのよりも少し甘い……",
      "startTime": 193.0220045887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_01-ngs021.m4a",
      "text": "同じブランドの桃なのに甘さに違いがあるんですね\nやっぱり熟してる桃の方が甘いのかな？",
      "startTime": 206.4886702381,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cooking-04.m4a",
          "delay": 3011.329761899987,
          "startTime": 209.5
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cooking-04.m4a",
          "delay": 2244.6630951999964,
          "startTime": 208.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
